{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"URLSearchParams.entries()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/entries","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URL_API\">URL API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/append\"><code>append()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/delete\"><code>delete()</code></a></li><li><em><code>entries()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/forEach\"><code>forEach()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/get\"><code>get()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/getAll\"><code>getAll()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/has\"><code>has()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/keys\"><code>keys()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/set\"><code>set()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/sort\"><code>sort()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/toString\"><code>toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/values\"><code>values()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for URL API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>URL</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p><code><strong>URLSearchParams.entries()</strong></code>方法返回一个<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Iteration_protocols\"><code>iterator</code></a>，允许遍历该对象中包含的所有键/值对。每一组键值对都是&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb\"><code>USVString</code></a>对象</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>注意</strong>: 该方法在&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a>也是可用的。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">searchParams.entries();</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>返回一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Iteration_protocols\"><code>iterator</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js;highlight:[5] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// 创建一个测试用 URLSearchParams 对象</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> searchParams <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">URLSearchParams</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"key1=value1&amp;key2=value2\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 显示键/值对</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> pair <span class=\"token keyword\">of</span> searchParams<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">entries</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>pair<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">', '</span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span> pair<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>结果如下：</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">key1, value1\nkey2, value2</pre>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.URLSearchParams.entries","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/entries/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另请参阅","title":"另请参阅","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>其他 URL 相关接口: <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>URL</code></a>, <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>URLUtils</code></a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"另请参阅","id":"另请参阅"}],"summary":"URLSearchParams.entries()方法返回一个iterator，允许遍历该对象中包含的所有键/值对。每一组键值对都是 USVString对象","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"URLSearchParams.entries()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"URLSearchParams.entries()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"URLSearchParams.entries()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/urlsearchparams/entries","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/urlsearchparams/entries/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams","title":"URLSearchParams"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/entries","title":"URLSearchParams.entries()"}],"pageTitle":"URLSearchParams.entries() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}